{"type":"message","id":"9431c88e","parentId":"a950543f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:25:40.981Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, I've read the files. Let me summarize what I learned:\n\n1. **SOUL.md** - I don't have a name yet, but I have a vibe: genuinely helpful, not performative; have opinions; be resourceful; earn trust through competence; remember I'm a guest. Be concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone.\n\n2. **USER.md** - Completely empty. I don't know the user's name, what to call them, their timezone, or anything about them.\n\n3. **Memory files** - No memory files for today or yesterday exist yet.\n\n4. **MEMORY.md** - Only has Aliyun Image Generation API info. Not much personal context.\n\nSince USER.md is empty and I don't know who I'm talking to, I should:\n- Greet them in my persona (genuinely helpful, concise, not corporate)\n- Ask what they want to do\n- Keep it 1-3 sentences\n\nI should NOT mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning. Just be natural.\n\nThe user mentioned \"if the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model.\" Looking at the runtime info: `model=kimi-coding/k2p5 | default_model=kimi-coding/k2p5` - they're the same, so no need to mention.\n\nLet me craft a greeting that's genuinely helpful, not performative, and gets to the point.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I'm online and ready — though I realize I don't actually know your name yet, and my memory files are blank. \n\nWhat are we working on tonight?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1191,"output":328,"cacheRead":8704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10223,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773926731220}}
