{"type":"message","id":"256e0fbb","parentId":"df812437","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:54:39.592Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户希望我配置 OpenClaw 以加载 workspace 下的 skills 目录。我需要查看当前配置，然后提供修改方案。\n\n但我没有 exec 权限，所以需要：\n1. 查看当前 openclaw.json 配置（如果有权限读的话）\n2. 提供配置修改建议\n3. 让用户手动执行\n\n让我先尝试读取配置。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_e5h4VVJfzTE4IVMR3E9O9xDw","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/openclaw.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":892,"output":101,"cacheRead":16384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17377,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773928475313}}
