{"type":"message","id":"d1ebd766","parentId":"99a897c4","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:54:50.204Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我无法直接读取 openclaw.json，因为路径在 sandbox 之外。但我可以提供一个配置方案，告诉用户如何修改。\n\nOpenClaw 的配置通常在 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`。要让 workspace 的 skills 目录被加载，需要在配置中添加 skills 路径。\n\n让我创建一个配置示例文件。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我来提供一个配置方案。OpenClaw 的配置文件在 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`，你需要手动修改它来添加 workspace skills 路径。\n\n**你需要在终端执行以下操作：**\n\n```bash\n# 1. 备份原配置\ncp ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.backup\n\n# 2. 编辑配置，添加 workspace skills 路径\n# 在 agents.wechat-assistant 或全局 skills 配置中添加路径\n```\n\n**配置示例（添加到 openclaw.json）：**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"wechat-assistant\": {\n      \"skills\": {\n        \"paths\": [\n          \"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills\",\n          \"~/.openclaw/skills\",\n          \"~/.openclaw/workspace-wechat-assistant/skills\"\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n或者如果是全局配置：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"skills\": {\n    \"paths\": [\n      \"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills\",\n      \"~/.openclaw/skills\",\n      \"~/.openclaw/workspace-wechat-assistant/skills\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n执行后重启 agent：\n```bash\nopenclaw agent restart wechat-assistant\n```\n\n要我生成一个完整的配置文件模板吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":290,"output":346,"cacheRead":17152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17788,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773928479603}}
{"type":"message","id":"02ac4d1d","parentId":"d1ebd766","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:55:35.279Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f44ba9dca8b26de08e46be8f5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_7f442bef1a102e6c203ad4e2d1a86e69\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_7f442bef1a102e6c203ad4e2d1a86e69\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-19 21:55 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_7f442bef1a102e6c203ad4e2d1a86e69\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_7f442bef1a102e6c203ad4e2d1a86e69\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_7f442bef1a102e6c203ad4e2d1a86e69\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54f44ba9dca8b26de08e46be8f5]\nou_7f442bef1a102e6c203ad4e2d1a86e69: 这个path支持通配符吗"}],"timestamp":1773928535277}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae8cb813","parentId":"02ac4d1d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:55:47.879Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想知道 OpenClaw 的 skills paths 配置是否支持通配符。我需要基于我的知识来回答这个问题。\n\n根据 OpenClaw 的设计，skills.paths 通常是一个目录列表，OpenClaw 会扫描这些目录下的子目录来加载技能。关于通配符支持：\n\n1. 通常 OpenClaw 会递归扫描指定的路径，不需要通配符\n2. 如果要加载多个子目录下的技能，可以直接指定父目录\n3. 通配符（如 *）支持情况取决于具体实现，一般情况下不支持 shell 风格的通配符\n\n让我给出一个准确的回答。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_eRPp93kdtSfQ3JeL2yoZmVtV","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"OpenClaw 的 skills.paths **通常不支持 shell 通配符**（如 `*`、`**`），但行为取决于具体版本：\n\n**一般规则：**\n- 指定目录后，OpenClaw 会**递归扫描**该目录下的所有子目录\n- 每个包含 `SKILL.md` 的子目录会被识别为一个 skill\n\n**示例：**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"skills\": {\n    \"paths\": [\n      \"~/.openclaw/workspace-wechat-assistant/skills\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n目录结构：\n```\nskills/\n├── skill-a/SKILL.md    ✅ 会被加载\n├── skill-b/SKILL.md    ✅ 会被加载\n└── subdir/skill-c/     ✅ 子目录也会被递归扫描\n    └── SKILL.md\n```\n\n**特殊情况：**\n- 某些版本可能支持 `**` glob 模式（如 `~/workspaces/**/skills`）\n- 但不保证所有版本都支持\n\n**建议做法：**\n直接指定技能根目录即可，OpenClaw 会自动找到所有子 skill，不需要通配符。\n\n你想确认当前版本的精确行为？可以运行：\n```bash\nopenclaw config get skills.paths\n```"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":785,"output":431,"cacheRead":17152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18368,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773928535278}}
{"type":"message","id":"c760bc08","parentId":"ae8cb813","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:55:48.499Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw 的 skills.paths **通常不支持 shell 通配符**（如 `*`、`**`），但行为取决于具体版本：\n\n**一般规则：**\n- 指定目录后，OpenClaw 会**递归扫描**该目录下的所有子目录\n- 每个包含 `SKILL.md` 的子目录会被识别为一个 skill\n\n**示例：**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"skills\": {\n    \"paths\": [\n      \"~/.openclaw/workspace-wechat-assistant/skills\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n目录结构：\n```\nskills/\n├── skill-a/SKILL.md    ✅ 会被加载\n├── skill-b/SKILL.md    ✅ 会被加载\n└── subdir/skill-c/     ✅ 子目录也会被递归扫描\n    └── SKILL.md\n```\n\n**特殊情况：**\n- 某些版本可能支持 `**` glob 模式（如 `~/workspaces/**/skills`）\n- 但不保证所有版本都支持\n\n**建议做法：**\n直接指定技能根目录即可，OpenClaw 会自动找到所有子 skill，不需要通配符。\n\n你想确认当前版本的精确行为？可以运行：\n```bash\nopenclaw config get skills.paths\n```"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773928548499}}
