{"type":"message","id":"7dadfa32","parentId":"1737a4d6","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:30:01.589Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我刚才已经回答过这个问题了。用户可能是想确认，或者想让我重新列出当前的技能状态。\n\n让我再列出一次清晰的技能列表。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**当前可用的 12 个技能：**\n\n**飞书系列（4个）：**\n- feishu-doc — 文档读写\n- feishu-drive — 云盘管理\n- feishu-perm — 权限管理\n- feishu-wiki — 知识库\n\n**工具类（4个）：**\n- clawhub — 技能市场（搜索/安装/更新）\n- weather — 天气查询\n- http — HTTP请求\n- skill-creator — 技能创建/审计\n\n**代理类（3个）：**\n- coding-agent — 代码任务代理（Codex/Claude）\n- healthcheck — 主机安全加固\n- node-connect — 节点连接诊断\n\n**网络搜索（1个）：**\n- agent-reach — 全网搜索（Twitter/Reddit/抖音/小红书等14个平台）\n\n**未激活（在 workspace 里）：**\n- my-workspace-skill — 示例技能，需配置路径后加载\n\n需要我详细介绍哪个技能，或者帮你配置加载 workspace 里的技能？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":875,"output":253,"cacheRead":18432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19560,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773930594092}}
